    "image_with_text_NjQ3EM": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_ENV8fL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Q:  What’s your advice for anyone looking to get into photography?</h3><p>A: Definitely find other creatives who also want to make a portfolio and collaborate with them. You basically want to create the work that you want to shoot.</p><h3>Q:  Where do you go when you are looking for inspiration?</h3><p>A: Basically nature, I like to walk down to the seawall to look at the water and look at the skies. I also try to get to art galleries when I can.</p><p></p><h3>Q: What is the most rewarding part of your job?</h3><p>A: The most rewarding part of my job is hearing how people interpret my photos. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_ENV8fL"
      ],
